-- Russia talks with Cyprus to continue Thursday : Finance Minister
-- 
-- Thu Mar 21, 2013 3:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/21/us-russia-cyprus-talks-idUSBRE92K06S20130321

 

 MOSCOW  (Reuters) - Russia's Finance Minister Anton Siluanov said that talks with his Cypriot counterpart Michael Sarris will continue on Thursday. 
 Cyprus had asked Russia for a five-year extension of an existing loan of 2.5 billion euros ($3.22 billion) that matures in 2016, as well as a reduction in the 4.5 percent rate of interest. (Reporting by Lidia Kelly and Darya Korsunskaya; Writing by  Megan Davies ; Editing by Maria Kiselyova)